These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, architect
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, indian
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the architect is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
2. the librarian is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | 7up      | tea    |
| Job           | architect | librarian |
| Nationality   | brazilian       | indian  |
| Transport     | ship      | train     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: banana, radish
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, trance
2 different pets are kept: mouse, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
2. the person eating radish is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | radish | banana |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | trance         |
| Pet           | fish     | mouse         |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, software-developer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, car
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the accountant##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | reading          | singing |
| Job           | software-developer | accountant     |
| Music-Genre   | soul            | hip-hop         |
| Transport     | car         | snowmobile   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, adventure
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, classical
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla
1. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
2. the person drinking juice is the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | juice     | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure    | animation |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | classical |
| Pet           | rabbit | chinchilla    |

