.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, cherry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, indie
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, train
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of blues is the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | mirinda |
| Food          | cherry   | pumpkin |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | blues     |
| Transport     | bike | train     |

 